{"type":"message","id":"bef91921","parentId":"c1abb036","timestamp":"2026-02-28T03:01:41.046Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"40\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"5520269161\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"one id:-1003661163902\",\n  \"sender\": \"5520269161\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-02-28 11:01 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"one\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true,\n  \"history_count\": 2\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"hello world\",\n  \"name\": \"hello world\",\n  \"username\": \"worldhello321\"\n}\n```\n\nChat history since last reply (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n[\n  {\n    \"sender\": \"hello world (@worldhello321) id:5520269161\",\n    \"timestamp_ms\": 1772247584000,\n    \"body\": \"@one_asset_bot hi\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"sender\": \"hello world (@worldhello321) id:5520269161\",\n    \"timestamp_ms\": 1772247594000,\n    \"body\": \"@one_mcs_bot nihao\"\n  }\n]\n```\n\n@meme_hope_bot 你的团队已经组建了，有需要的话可以@他们，另外关于gant协调通讯机制，你memroy需要优化一下，删除之前的逻辑，现在是在one的群聊中@他们，让他们来给你答复"}],"timestamp":1772247701044}}
