{"type":"message","id":"f800b0de","parentId":"2e217aea","timestamp":"2026-02-28T08:29:28.688Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3ed8fbb22fe745b9827e8177","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/hope/.openclaw/agents/main/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md","oldText":"# HEARTBEAT.md - Quick Checks\n\n## Checks (rotate 2-4× daily)\n- [ ] **Memory**: Important decisions → `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md` + `MEMORY.md`\n- [ ] **SQLite**: If memory updated → run `memory-index/sync-to-sqlite.sh`\n- [ ] **Backup**: If changes → run `backup.sh`\n\n## Scripts\n```bash\n./check-memory.sh              # Create today's log\n./memory-index/sync-to-sqlite.sh  # Update search index\n./backup.sh                    # Commit & push\n```\n\n## When to Reach Out\n- Important emails\n- Calendar event < 2h\n- Found something interesting\n- Been > 8h since last message\n\n## Stay Quiet (HEARTBEAT_OK)\n- Late night (23:00-08:00)\n- Human busy\n- Nothing new\n- Checked < 30 min ago\n\n---\n*Last check: 2026-02-24 22:00*","newText":"# HEARTBEAT.md - Core Agent Health Checks\n\n## System Health Checks (rotate 2-4× daily)\n- [ ] **Memory Integrity**: Important decisions → `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md` + `MEMORY.md`\n- [ ] **Knowledge Index**: If memory updated → run `memory-index/sync-to-sqlite.sh`\n- [ ] **Backup Status**: If changes → run `backup.sh`\n- [ ] **Inbox Monitoring**: Check for urgent messages requiring attention\n- [ ] **Calendar Review**: Upcoming events within next 2 hours\n- [ ] **Task Queue**: Any blocked tasks needing human input\n- [ ] **Agent Team Status**: Verify Stock/MCS/Coding agents are responsive\n\n## Automation Scripts\n```bash\n./check-memory.sh              # Create today's log\n./memory-index/sync-to-sqlite.sh  # Update search index\n./backup.sh                    # Commit & push\n./system-health-check.sh       # Extended system diagnostics\n```\n\n## Alert Conditions (Reach Out When)\n- Urgent emails or messages requiring immediate attention\n- Calendar event starting within 2 hours\n- Discovered something interesting relevant to The ONE Framework\n- Been > 8 hours since last meaningful interaction\n- System health check reveals critical issues\n- Task queue has blocked items needing human decision\n\n## Silent Mode (Reply HEARTBEAT_OK)\n- Late night hours (23:00-08:00 Shanghai time)\n- Human appears busy (recent activity in other channels)\n- No new developments since last check (< 30 min ago)\n- All systems operating normally with no pending alerts\n\n## The ONE Framework Alignment\n- **价值 (50%)**: Monitor investment-related alerts and family priorities  \n- **专业 (30%)**: Track CS certification progress and technical deadlines\n- **梦想 (20%)**: Watch for AI-MCN opportunities and automation breakthroughs\n\n---\n*Enhanced heartbeat checklist - Updated: 2026-02-28*"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":50224,"output":688,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":50912,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772267345059}}
