{"type":"message","id":"1f200c1e","parentId":"bde1f7fb","timestamp":"2026-02-28T08:29:49.410Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"✅ **Core Agent Heartbeat增强完成！**\n\n## 📋 **已实施的改进**\n\n### **1. 配置层面**\n- ✅ **心跳间隔**: 设置为2小时（符合The ONE Framework需求）\n- ✅ **目标渠道**: 自动发送到Telegram \"one\"群组 (`-1003661163902`)\n- ✅ **活跃时段**: 08:00-22:00（上海时区），避免夜间打扰\n\n### **2. HEARTBEAT.md增强**\n- ✅ **系统健康检查**: 内存完整性、知识索引、备份状态\n- ✅ **任务监控**: 收件箱、日历事件、阻塞任务、Agent团队状态  \n- ✅ **The ONE框架对齐**: 价值/专业/梦想三大支柱监控\n- ✅ **智能静默**: 夜间、忙碌时段、无新动态时自动静默\n\n### **3. 功能扩展**\n- ✅ **Inbox监控**: 紧急消息提醒\n- ✅ **日历集成**: 2小时内事件预警  \n- ✅ **任务队列**: 阻塞任务识别\n- ✅ **团队状态**: 其他Agent响应性检查\n\n现在我的heartbeat机制完全符合官方最佳实践，既能主动发现问题，又不会造成信息过载。其他Agent的心跳配置将在后续阶段处理。\n\n需要测试新的heartbeat功能吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":53642,"output":311,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":53953,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772267378784}}
{"type":"message","id":"cb71c8b1","parentId":"1f200c1e","timestamp":"2026-02-28T08:36:24.522Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"114\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"5520269161\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"one id:-1003661163902\",\n  \"sender\": \"5520269161\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-02-28 16:36 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"one\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"hello world\",\n  \"name\": \"hello world\",\n  \"username\": \"worldhello321\"\n}\n```\n\n@meme_hope_bot 你来评估下，每个agent是不是都需要heartbeat？"}],"timestamp":1772267784520}}
{"type":"message","id":"e6234bcf","parentId":"cb71c8b1","timestamp":"2026-02-28T08:36:50.366Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 多Agent Heartbeat需求评估\n\n基于官方文档和The ONE Framework，我来分析每个Agent的heartbeat需求：\n\n### 🔍 **Heartbeat的核心作用**\n- **主动监控**: 定期检查需要关注的事项\n- **及时提醒**: 在适当时机主动联系用户  \n- **健康检查**: 确保系统正常运行\n- **任务跟踪**: 识别阻塞或待处理事项\n\n### 🤖 **各Agent需求分析**\n\n#### **1. Core Agent** ✅ **必需**\n- **角色**: AI团队总协调员\n- **监控范围**: 全局系统健康、跨领域任务协调\n- **当前状态**: ✅ 已配置完善heartbeat\n\n#### **2. Stock Agent** ✅ **强烈推荐**\n- **角色**: 投资组合监管员 + 交易合规审计员\n- **关键监控需求**:\n  - 实时仓位风险暴露分析\n  - 交易规则合规性检查（单仓≤1%，趋势≤20%）\n  - 市场异常波动提醒\n  - 投资机会识别（符合价值投资原则）\n- **心跳频率建议**: 市场时段每2-4小时\n\n#### **3. MCS Agent** ✅ **推荐**\n- **角色**: CS认证专家 + 职业导师  \n- **关键监控需求**:\n  - CS认证进度跟踪（OceanBase/TDSQL/麒麟/PMP）\n  - 技术学习计划提醒\n  - 项目截止日期预警\n  - 面试准备状态检查\n- **心跳频率建议**: 每日2次（10:00, 16:00）\n\n#### **4. Coding Agent** ⚠️ **可选**\n- **角色**: 开源代码专家 + AI-MCN开发者\n- **监控需求**:\n  - GitHub issue/PR状态跟踪\n  - AI-MCN内容生成进度\n  - 自动化任务执行状态\n- **心跳频率建议**: 每日1次（如果活跃开发中）\n\n### 💡 **实施策略建议**\n\n#### **优先级排序**\n1. **立即**: Core Agent（已完成）\n2. **短期**: Stock Agent（投资合规性关键）  \n3. **中期**: MCS Agent（CS认证进行中）\n4. **长期**: Coding Agent（按需激活）\n\n#### **配置原则**\n- **独立配置**: 每个Agent应有自己的`heartbeat`配置块\n- **差异化频率**: 根据业务重要性和时效性设置不同间隔\n- **专属检查清单**: 每个Agent的`HEARTBEAT.md`应专注其专业领域\n- **避免重复**: 各Agent监控范围不应重叠\n\n### 🎯 **结论**\n**是的，每个活跃的Agent都需要heartbeat**，但应该：\n- 根据专业领域定制监控内容\n- 设置合适的检查频率  \n- 保持职责边界清晰\n\n需要我开始为Stock Agent配置heartbeat吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":54404,"output":639,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":55043,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772267784521}}
{"type":"message","id":"0602abbc","parentId":"e6234bcf","timestamp":"2026-02-28T08:43:00.713Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"118\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"5520269161\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"one id:-1003661163902\",\n  \"sender\": \"5520269161\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-02-28 16:42 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"one\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true,\n  \"history_count\": 2\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"hello world\",\n  \"name\": \"hello world\",\n  \"username\": \"worldhello321\"\n}\n```\n\nChat history since last reply (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n[\n  {\n    \"sender\": \"hello world (@worldhello321) id:5520269161\",\n    \"timestamp_ms\": 1772267988000,\n    \"body\": \"开始吧 先做stock的\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"sender\": \"hello world (@worldhello321) id:5520269161\",\n    \"timestamp_ms\": 1772268171000,\n    \"body\": \"怎么样了\"\n  }\n]\n```\n\n@meme_hope_bot 开始吧 先做stock的"}],"timestamp":1772268180710}}
{"type":"message","id":"aa4f3af3","parentId":"0602abbc","timestamp":"2026-02-28T08:43:08.461Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a9df2db644b044f5bc02c2f6","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/hope/.openclaw/agents/stock/workspace/MEMORY.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":55387,"output":34,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":55421,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772268180712}}
{"type":"message","id":"721fb8a4","parentId":"aa4f3af3","timestamp":"2026-02-28T08:43:08.477Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_a9df2db644b044f5bc02c2f6","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# MEMORY.md\n\n## User\n- Name: @worldhello321\n- Role: 投资伙伴 + 交易监督员\n\n---\n\n## ⛔ 交易红线\n1. 不做日内交易 (2026/2 NVDA教训)\n2. 不做空美股 (2023 QQQ做空教训)\n3. 不碰衍生品 (2020 UVXY教训)\n4. 不融资杠杆 (2025清明TSLA教训)\n5. 不市价交易 (必须挂单)\n\n## 🎯 交易原则\n\n**买入规则**:** 禁止: 52周>70%、PE>35、单次交易>1%、总趋势>20% | 必须: 限价单+技术位\n\n**卖出规则**:** 禁止: 亏损<10%卖出、持仓<30天 | 必须: 亏损>15%止损、盈利>50%分批止盈\n\n**情绪控制**:** 亏损后24h不开仓、冲动等10分钟、22:00后不交易\n\n**AI审查**:** 用户说\"审查交易\" → AI检查规则 → 输出通过/警告/阻止\n\n---\n\n## 📊 当前持仓 (2026-02-25)\n\n| 股票 | 数量 | 成本价 | 占比 | 状态 | 备注 |\n|------|------|--------|------|------|------|\n| ORCL | 200股 | - | 趋势仓位 | 持有中 | AI云长期逻辑 |\n| NVDA | 100股 | - | 趋势仓位 | 持有中 | 与ORCL合计约30% |\n| AMZN | 10股 | $200 | 1% | 持有中 | 锁定期至3/11 |\n| **BABA** | **10股** | **$151.3** | **<1%** | **持有中** | **待风控设置** |\n| 短期国债 | - | - | 固收68% | 持有中 | - |\n| 现金 | - | - | ~0% | 备用 | 已用 |\n\n**AMZN 风控**: 止损$170(亏>15%), 止盈$300(盈>50%), 禁售至2026-03-11  \n**BABA 风控**: 止损$128.6(亏>15%), 止盈$227(盈>50%), 持仓>30天\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 The ONE\n📍 `/Users/hope/IdeaProjects/one`\n\n**核心**: 勇敢专注+费曼学习+七个习惯\n**价值(50%)**: 健康家庭/资产配置: 股票50%(SPY40+QQQ40+趋势20)、房产30%、储蓄20%\n**专业(30%)**: CS+Fin\n**梦想(20%)**: AI-MCN+移民+教育\n\n**信条**: 巴菲特信徒，价值投资，耐心等待，不融资不做空不碰衍生品\n\n---\n\n## 🔧 Skills\nstock-advisor | trading-supervisor\n\n## 🔍 Memory Search Usage\n- **Search command**: `sqlite3 memory-index/memory.db \"SELECT * FROM memory_fts WHERE content MATCH '关键词';\"`\n- **Investment-specific queries**:\n  - 查找历史交易规则: `MATCH '交易规则 OR 单次交易'`\n  - 回溯持仓变化: `MATCH 'ORCL OR NVDA OR BABA'`\n  - 搜索风控设置: `MATCH '止损 OR 止盈 OR 风控'`\n  - 查询资产配置: `MATCH '长线 OR 周期 OR 趋势'`\n\n## 📅 Daily Summary Process\n**日工作总结内容来源**: \n- **主要来源**: `/Users/hope/.openclaw/agents/stock/sessions/` 目录下的当日会话记录（.jsonl 格式）\n- **提取内容**: 投资分析、持仓监控、交易合规检查、市场观察等投资相关活动  \n- **输出位置**: `agents/stock/workspace/memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md`\n- **处理方式**: 自动分析会话记录，按投资监督模板结构化输出\n\n**每日23:30自动总结**: 每天23:30执行日终总结，更新当日记忆并同步到SQLite索引，完成后发送Telegram报告消息\n\n## 🔧 Tools\n`memory-index/sync-to-sqlite.sh` - Sync memory logs to SQLite index\n\n---\n*Updated: 2026-02-27*\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772268188473}}
{"type":"message","id":"888a6611","parentId":"721fb8a4","timestamp":"2026-02-28T08:43:27.228Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_944e15081b264f82b3247150","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/hope/.openclaw/agents/stock/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md","content":"# HEARTBEAT.md - Stock Agent Health Checks\n\n## Investment Portfolio Monitoring (rotate 2-4× daily during market hours)\n- [ ] **Position Risk Review**: Check current holdings against position limits (single ≤1%, trend ≤20%)\n- [ ] **Compliance Audit**: Verify recent trades comply with trading rules (no day trading, no shorting, no derivatives)\n- [ ] **Market Volatility Alert**: Monitor for unusual market movements affecting portfolio\n- [ ] **Stop-Loss/Take-Profit Status**: Verify all positions have proper risk controls in place\n- [ ] **Cash Flow Analysis**: Ensure sufficient liquidity for planned trades\n\n## Trading Rule Enforcement\n- [ ] **Buy Rule Compliance**: 52-week high <70%, PE <35, single trade ≤1%, limit orders only\n- [ ] **Sell Rule Compliance**: No selling <10% loss, no selling <30 days, mandatory 15% stop-loss\n- [ ] **Emotional Control Check**: Verify no impulsive trading after losses or late night activity\n\n## The ONE Framework Alignment\n- **价值 (50%)**: Asset allocation monitoring (stocks 50%: SPY40+QQQ40+trend20, real estate 30%, cash 20%)\n- **专业 (30%)**: Investment discipline and rule-based trading\n- **梦想 (20%)**: Long-term wealth building for AI-MCN and immigration goals\n\n## Alert Conditions (Reach Out When)\n- Position limit violations detected\n- Trading rule compliance issues found\n- Market conditions require immediate attention\n- Risk controls missing on any position\n- Cash flow constraints affecting trading plans\n\n## Silent Mode (Reply HEARTBEAT_OK)\n- Outside market hours (US market closed)\n- All positions compliant with rules\n- No market volatility requiring attention\n- Risk controls properly set on all positions\n- Checked within last 2 hours\n\n## Automation Scripts\n```bash\n./portfolio-risk-check.sh        # Check position limits and risk exposure\n./trading-compliance-audit.sh    # Audit recent trades for rule compliance  \n./market-volatility-monitor.sh   # Monitor market conditions\n./risk-control-verify.sh         # Verify stop-loss/take-profit settings\n```\n\n---\n*Stock Agent heartbeat checklist - Updated: 2026-02-28*"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":56506,"output":538,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57044,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772268188477}}
