tility requiring attention\n- Risk controls properly set on all positions\n- Checked within last 2 hours\n\n## Automation Scripts\n```bash\n./portfolio-risk-check.sh        # Check position limits and risk exposure\n./trading-compliance-audit.sh    # Audit recent trades for rule compliance  \n./market-volatility-monitor.sh   # Monitor market conditions\n./risk-control-verify.sh         # Verify stop-loss/take-profit settings\n```\n\n---\n*Stock Agent heartbeat checklist - Updated: 2026-02-28*\nEOF"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":60404,"output":560,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":60964,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772268576740}}
