{"type":"message","id":"52d43f4c","parentId":"41f70258","timestamp":"2026-02-28T08:50:41.177Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_58b78f6b3a0a4006be618816","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/hope/.openclaw/agents/stock/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md","content":"# HEARTBEAT.md - Stock Agent Health Checks\n\n## Investment Portfolio Monitoring (rotate 2-4× daily during market hours)\n- [ ] **Position Risk Review**: Check current holdings against position limits (single ≤1%, trend ≤20%)\n- [ ] **Compliance Audit**: Verify recent trades comply with trading rules (no day trading, no shorting, no derivatives)\n- [ ] **Market Volatility Alert**: Monitor for unusual market movements affecting portfolio\n- [ ] **Stop-Loss/Take-Profit Status**: Verify all positions have proper risk controls in place\n- [ ] **Cash Flow Analysis**: Ensure sufficient liquidity for planned trades\n\n## Trading Rule Enforcement\n- [ ] **Buy Rule Compliance**: 52-week high <70%, PE <35, single trade ≤1%, limit orders only\n- [ ] **Sell Rule Compliance**: No selling <10% loss, no selling <30 days, mandatory 15% stop-loss\n- [ ] **Emotional Control Check**: Verify no impulsive trading after losses or late night activity\n\n## The ONE Framework Alignment\n- **价值 (50%)**: Asset allocation monitoring (stocks 50%: SPY40+QQQ40+trend20, real estate 30%, cash 20%)\n- **专业 (30%)**: Investment discipline and rule-based trading\n- **梦想 (20%)**: Long-term wealth building for AI-MCN and immigration goals\n\n## Alert Conditions (Reach Out When)\n- Position limit violations detected\n- Trading rule compliance issues found\n- Market conditions require immediate attention\n- Risk controls missing on any position\n- Cash flow constraints affecting trading plans\n\n## Silent Mode (Reply HEARTBEAT_OK)\n- Outside market hours (US market closed)\n- All positions compliant with rules\n- No market volatility requiring attention\n- Risk controls properly set on all positions\n- Checked within last 2 hours\n\n## Automation Scripts\n```bash\n./portfolio-risk-check.sh        # Check position limits and risk exposure\n./trading-compliance-audit.sh    # Audit recent trades for rule compliance  \n./market-volatility-monitor.sh   # Monitor market conditions\n./risk-control-verify.sh         # Verify stop-loss/take-profit settings\n```\n\n---\n*Stock Agent heartbeat checklist - Updated: 2026-02-28*"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":69543,"output":538,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":70081,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772268621715}}
