{"type":"message","id":"93051275","parentId":"bf0e3159","timestamp":"2026-02-28T10:02:47.435Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"在OpenClaw的安全架构中，**不能直接给其他Agent临时授权访问 `~/IdeaProjects`**，但有几种替代方案：\n\n## 🔒 **安全限制原因**\n- **工作区隔离**: 每个Agent只能访问自己的workspace\n- **最小权限原则**: 防止意外或恶意操作\n- **系统安全**: 保护用户项目和数据\n\n## 🔄 **推荐的协作模式**\n\n### **方案1: Core Agent代理操作（推荐）**\n- **Coding Agent** → **请求Core Agent** → **Core Agent执行操作**\n- Coding Agent可以发送请求给我，我来执行 `~/IdeaProjects` 相关操作\n- 保持安全隔离，同时实现功能\n\n### **方案2: 项目文件同步**\n- 将需要的文件从 `~/IdeaProjects` 复制到 Coding Agent的workspace\n- Coding Agent在其workspace内操作\n- 完成后我可以将结果同步回原项目\n\n### **方案3: 会话级临时访问**\n- 在特定会话中，我可以spawn一个具有扩展权限的子agent\n- 用于一次性任务，完成后自动清理\n\n## 💡 **实际操作建议**\n对于Coding Agent的典型需求：\n- **代码分析**: 我可以读取文件并提供给Coding Agent\n- **项目修改**: Coding Agent提供修改建议，我来执行\n- **构建部署**: 我可以执行构建脚本并将结果反馈给Coding Agent\n\n**这种设计确保了安全性，同时通过Core Agent协调实现了完整的功能。**\n\n需要我为Coding Agent的某个具体任务设置这种协作模式吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":85427,"output":344,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":85771,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772272951822}}
{"type":"message","id":"6f64f1cc","parentId":"93051275","timestamp":"2026-03-01T01:10:44.845Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"154\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"5520269161\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"one id:-1003661163902\",\n  \"sender\": \"5520269161\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-03-01 09:10 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"one\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true,\n  \"history_count\": 5\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"hello world\",\n  \"name\": \"hello world\",\n  \"username\": \"worldhello321\"\n}\n```\n\nChat history since last reply (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n[\n  {\n    \"sender\": \"hello world (@worldhello321) id:5520269161\",\n    \"timestamp_ms\": 1772326848000,\n    \"body\": \"@one_coding_bot 你有每日工作总结的事项吗\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"sender\": \"hello world (@worldhello321) id:5520269161\",\n    \"timestamp_ms\": 1772326891000,\n    \"body\": \"中文回答\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"sender\": \"hello world (@worldhello321) id:5520269161\",\n    \"timestamp_ms\": 1772326906000,\n    \"body\": \"@one_coding_bot 中文回复\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"sender\": \"hello world (@worldhello321) id:5520269161\",\n    \"timestamp_ms\": 1772327024000,\n    \"body\": \"@one_coding_bot 你的工作总结每天什么时间、会发送总结报告到群里吗\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"sender\": \"hello world (@worldhello321) id:5520269161\",\n    \"timestamp_ms\": 1772327324000,\n    \"body\": \"@one_coding_bot 你看下你每天什么时间进行工作总结，\"\n  }\n]\n```\n\n@meme_hope_bot 你没有设置coding的工作总结吗，我看mcs和stock有的"}],"timestamp":1772327444842}}
