{"type":"message","id":"2ed68048","parentId":"da7a2a64","timestamp":"2026-03-01T01:11:34.875Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"你说得对！我确实**没有为Coding Agent配置每日工作总结**。让我检查一下其他Agent的配置：\n\n## 🔍 **当前状态分析**\n\n### ✅ **Stock Agent & MCS Agent**\n- 都有完整的**每日工作总结机制**\n- 会在**23:30自动执行**日终总结\n- 生成结构化报告并发送到Telegram群组\n\n### ❌ **Coding Agent**\n- **缺少每日工作总结配置**\n- 虽然有`MEMORY.md`定义了职责，但没有自动化总结流程\n- 没有配置heartbeat来触发日常总结\n\n## 📋 **需要补充的配置**\n\n### **1. Coding Agent HEARTBEAT.md**\n需要创建专门的心跳检查清单，包含：\n- GitHub issue监控状态\n- PR提交和审核进度  \n- 开源贡献统计\n- 代码质量检查\n\n### **2. 每日总结自动化脚本**\n- 每日23:30自动执行\n- 从会话记录提取coding相关活动\n- 生成贡献报告并发送到群组\n\n### **3. Heartbeat配置**\n- 配置适当的检查频率（建议每4小时）\n- 设置活跃时段（覆盖开发时间）\n\n## 🔧 **立即行动**\n让我为Coding Agent配置完整的工作总结机制！\n\n"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":97581,"output":279,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":97860,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772327480622}}
{"type":"message","id":"6ef0b987","parentId":"2ed68048","timestamp":"2026-03-01T01:12:59.376Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"158\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"5520269161\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"one id:-1003661163902\",\n  \"sender\": \"5520269161\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-03-01 09:12 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"one\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true,\n  \"history_count\": 1\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"hello world\",\n  \"name\": \"hello world\",\n  \"username\": \"worldhello321\"\n}\n```\n\nChat history since last reply (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n[\n  {\n    \"sender\": \"hello world (@worldhello321) id:5520269161\",\n    \"timestamp_ms\": 1772327561000,\n    \"body\": \"可以的，按这个方案来\"\n  }\n]\n```\n\n@meme_hope_bot 可以的，按这个方案来"}],"timestamp":1772327579374}}
{"type":"message","id":"a83c0a41","parentId":"6ef0b987","timestamp":"2026-03-01T01:13:42.955Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_881a61e83dc9421aac7e9e01","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/hope/.openclaw/agents/coding/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md","content":"# HEARTBEAT.md - Coding Agent Health Checks\n\n## Open Source Contribution Monitoring (rotate 2-4× daily)\n- [ ] **GitHub Issue Tracking**: Check assigned repositories for new issues requiring attention\n- [ ] **PR Status Review**: Monitor submitted pull requests for review feedback and merge status\n- [ ] **Contribution Progress**: Track coding contribution metrics and community recognition\n- [ ] **Code Quality Assurance**: Ensure all submissions pass CI/CD and follow project standards\n- [ ] **Community Engagement**: Monitor GitHub discussions and community interactions\n\n## Project Management Tasks\n- [ ] **Repository Monitoring**: Verify daily issue checks on assigned projects (OpenClaw Core)\n- [ ] **Issue Prioritization**: Review good first issue / help wanted labels for next tasks\n- [ ] **Documentation Updates**: Ensure technical documentation is current and accurate\n- [ ] **Skill Development**: Identify areas for improvement in coding expertise\n\n## The ONE Framework Alignment\n- **价值 (50%)**: Building open source reputation and technical portfolio\n- **专业 (30%)**: CS certification support through practical coding experience  \n- **梦想 (20%)**: AI-MCN content generation and automation development\n\n## Alert Conditions (Reach Out When)\n- New high-priority issues in assigned repositories\n- PR review feedback requiring immediate attention\n- CI/CD failures on submitted code\n- Community recognition or mentions from maintainers\n- Blocked tasks needing human input\n\n## Silent Mode (Reply HEARTBEAT_OK)\n- No new issues or PR activity since last check\n- All contributions progressing normally\n- Checked within last 4 hours\n- Outside active development hours (23:00-08:00)\n\n## Automation Scripts\n```bash\n./github-issue-monitor.sh     # Check for new issues in assigned repositories\n./pr-status-check.sh         # Monitor PR review and merge status  \n./contribution-metrics.sh    # Track coding contribution statistics\n./community-engagement.sh    # Monitor GitHub discussions and interactions\n```\n\n---\n*Coding Agent heartbeat checklist - Updated: 2026-03-01*"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":98146,"output":478,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":98624,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772327579375}}
