{"type":"message","id":"1dbb08c8","parentId":"020ce213","timestamp":"2026-03-02T00:26:50.203Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我发现了问题！Coding Agent的配置中存在两个关键问题：\n\n1. **HEARTBEAT.md文件为空** - 只有注释，没有实际的检查清单\n2. **heartbeat配置的目标地址不一致** - 配置中`to`字段指向了群组ID，但其他设置可能有问题\n\n让我修复这些问题：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_480c07bf506a4e268cb85bca","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/hope/.openclaw/agents/coding/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md","content":"# HEARTBEAT.md - Coding Agent Health Checks\n\n## Open Source Contribution Monitoring (rotate 2-4× daily)\n- [ ] **GitHub Issue Tracking**: Check assigned repositories for new issues requiring attention\n- [ ] **PR Status Review**: Monitor submitted pull requests for review feedback and merge status\n- [ ] **Contribution Progress**: Track coding contribution metrics and community recognition\n- [ ] **Code Quality Assurance**: Ensure all submissions pass CI/CD and follow project standards\n- [ ] **Community Engagement**: Monitor GitHub discussions and community interactions\n\n## Project Management Tasks\n- [ ] **Repository Monitoring**: Verify daily issue checks on assigned projects (OpenClaw Core)\n- [ ] **Issue Prioritization**: Review good first issue / help wanted labels for next tasks\n- [ ] **Documentation Updates**: Ensure technical documentation is current and accurate\n- [ ] **Skill Development**: Identify areas for improvement in coding expertise\n\n## The ONE Framework Alignment\n- **价值 (50%)**: Building open source reputation and technical portfolio\n- **专业 (30%)**: CS certification support through practical coding experience  \n- **梦想 (20%)**: AI-MCN content generation and automation development\n\n## Alert Conditions (Reach Out When)\n- New high-priority issues in assigned repositories\n- PR review feedback requiring immediate attention\n- CI/CD failures on submitted code\n- Community recognition or mentions from maintainers\n- Blocked tasks needing human input\n\n## Silent Mode (Reply HEARTBEAT_OK)\n- No new issues or PR activity since last check\n- All contributions progressing normally\n- Checked within last 4 hours\n- Outside active development hours (23:00-08:00)\n\n## Daily Summary Process\n**日工作总结内容来源**: \n- **主要来源**: `/Users/hope/.openclaw/agents/coding/sessions/` 目录下的当日会话记录（.jsonl 格式）\n- **提取内容**: GitHub issue监控、PR创建、代码审查、社区互动等开源贡献活动  \n- **输出位置**: `agents/coding/workspace/memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md`\n- **处理方式**: 自动分析会话记录，按开源贡献模板结构化输出\n\n**每日23:30自动总结**: 每天23:30执行日终总结，更新当日记忆并同步到SQLite索引，完成后发送Telegram报告消息\n\n## Automation Scripts\n```bash\n./github-issue-monitor.sh     # Check for new issues in assigned repositories\n./pr-status-check.sh         # Monitor PR review and merge status  \n./contribution-metrics.sh    # Track coding contribution statistics\n./community-engagement.sh    # Monitor GitHub discussions and interactions\n```\n\n---\n*Coding Agent heartbeat checklist - Updated: 2026-03-02*"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":115017,"output":698,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":115715,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772411182867}}
